net.bytebuddy.instrumentation

Class InvocationHandlerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.bytebuddy.instrumentation.InvocationHandlerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Instrumentation

    public abstract class InvocationHandlerAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements Instrumentation
    An adapter for adapting an InvocationHandler. The adapter allows the invocation handler to also intercept method calls to non-interface methods.

      • of

        public static Instrumentation of(java.lang.String fieldName)
        Creates an instrumentation for any InvocationHandler that delegates all method interceptions to a public instance field with the given name. This field has to be set before any invocations are intercepted. Otherwise, a NullPointerException will be thrown.
        Parameters:
        fieldName - The name of the field.
        Returns:
        An instrumentation that delegates all method interceptions to an instance field of the given name.
